title: Mad Games Tycoon v0.150509B
description:
Hotfix: 0.150509A + 0.150509B

0.150509B
- Different languages have been updated.
- Bug removed: Some objects could not be placed.
- Bug removed: You could put objects into other objects.
- Bug removed: Mintendu D-S discontinued 2013

0.150509A
- The game now uses the Unity5 Engine.
- If you stop the development of a engine, you get money back.
- Different languages have been updated.
- Bug removed: Cancel development of engines, now works again.
- Bug removed: Some plants were invisible.
- Bug removed: Fan letter bug fixed. (Core gamers / Casual gamers)
- Bug removed: If you're loaded a save game, some platforms have disappeared
